  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bca\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bc7\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0baf \u0bb5\u0bb3\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa\u0ba9\u0bc8 \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bcd\u0baf \u0bae\u0bc1\u0baf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf - \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bae\u0bb2\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Attempt to sell the country's assets and national resources - Vimal",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Apart from the fact that there is no necessary leadership to solve the economic crises that the country is currently facing, efforts are being made to sell the country's assets and national resources instead of solving these crises, said Vimal Weerawansa, the leader of the National Freedom Front and Member of Parliament.",
        "He further said that in such a situation, he is jointly researching the solutions to the crisis facing the country's economy, including the shortage of essential commodities including gas and fuel, and will publish the solutions found next week.",
        "He said the above while participating in a press conference organized in Colombo on Wednesday (06). There he added:",
        "As the country is currently facing a massive economic crisis, there is a dire need for leadership that can make moves towards recovery.",
        "But aside from the absence of such leadership now, efforts are being made to sell off the country's assets and national resources rather than resolving these crises.",
        "Prime Minister Ranil Wickramasinghe says that the Sri Lanka Petroleum Corporation is running on profit, but that burden cannot be imposed on the public.",
        "In that case, everyone should come together to solve this economic crisis that has affected all parties without any differences.",
        "Especially today (yesterday) a minister has resigned. It has to be looked at based on the reason.",
        "Such scams and policies are taking place in the current situation where the country is facing a massive crisis. Apart from this, allegations have already been made regarding the import of gas.",
        "Similarly, the presence of the Sri Lankan Navy in the North Sea is now reduced due to fuel shortages.",
        "Our fishermen also do not go to sea. As a result, Indian fishermen enter our waters and loot the marine resources.",
        "In such a background, even though we are on the opposite side, we are jointly exploring the solutions to the crisis facing the country's economy, including the shortage of essential commodities such as gas and fuel. He said that we will publish the solutions found through it next week."
      ],
